### Backend Key Files

- `main.py` - Application entry point, FastAPI app initialization
- `app/agents/orchestrator.py` - Coordinates AI agent pipeline
- `app/core/config.py` - Environment variables and settings
- `app/api/v1/*.py` - API route definitions

